n files show Epstein built a military-grade encrypted link to satellite orbit at Zorro Ranch. The contractor who built it now holds a Pentagon missile defense contract.", "large_image": "cpkRCzgQvHKkNnZu.png", "title": "Jeffrey Epstein Was CIA. The Communications Network at Zorro Ranch Proves It."}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "text", "uuid": "1ASsZ5tC9U", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 26, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8630014, "raw_content": "For all of you, you must understand Trump runs the government like a business. His disruptive policies and actions are like mergers & acquisitions (M&A).   M&A - he'll either put the head chopper in first, to get the hard work done despite opinion, then replace with a more \"subtle\" person.  That person goes in after the chopping is done and sets policy and smooths over the rough terrain.  Conversely he will put a \"subtle\" person in to re-arrange things \"softly\" and without fanfare, then replace them with the executor.\n\nI'll speak to the second instance.  He put Pam in as AG, she's a softer, subtler type of person, but she's a very thorough experienced prosecutor.  Her term was spent investigating and setting the table for the executioner - Blanche.\n\nWhat you're going to see from now until the midterms are indictments, prosecutions and a very large amount of convictions.  You all want justice, we get it, and you're about to see it pan out.  I told you making these cases takes time.  We as the prosecutor have to convince the 12 jurors beyond a reasonable doubt. We don't want to get to trial only to have some of these snakes and traitors walk.  We want 100% conviction rates.  That's what Pam spent her term doing.  She was investigating, impaneling grand juries and setting the table for the forthcoming trials.  Blanche is a stone cold killer.\n\nTiming here is important.  Trump needs the base energized for the mid-terms.  What better way to do this than toss some red meat out there with indictments arrests and trials of the people that have subverted and attacked this country the better part of 12 years now.  Trump NEVER forgets.  \n\nHe's going about this very  methodically and his timing is important.  I know you all get impatient with him and want this shit done like yesterday.  We understand.  However, there is a larger stategic play here.  Trust Trump.\n\nFrom now until the mid-terms will be very very interesting times.  Pay attention, Trump is always inside the OODA loop of the deep statists communists and RINOs.  Trust him.  He knows what he's doing.", "author": "Badfinz_FL", "created": 1779294834799, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "turdspolished-check", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Some inside baseball on what President Trump is doing - J6, 2020 Election, Russia Gate etc", "last_comment_created": 1779300932207, "content": "<p>For all of you, you must understand Trump runs the government like a business. His disruptive policies and actions are like mergers &amp; acquisitions (M&amp;A).   M&amp;A - he'll either put the head chopper in first, to get the hard work done despite opinion, then replace with a more &quot;subtle&quot; person.  That person goes in after the chopping is done and sets policy and smooths over the rough terrain.  Conversely he will put a &quot;subtle&quot; person in to re-arrange things &quot;softly&quot; and without fanfare, then replace them with the executor.</p>\n<p>I'll speak to the second instance.  He put Pam in as AG, she's a softer, subtler type of person, but she's a very thorough experienced prosecutor.  Her term was spent investigating and setting the table for the executioner - Blanche.</p>\n<p>What you're going to see from now until the midterms are indictments, prosecutions and a very large amount of convictions.  You all want justice, we get it, and you're about to see it pan out.  I told you making these cases takes time.  We as the prosecutor have to convince the 12 jurors beyond a reasonable doubt. We don't want to get to trial only to have some of these snakes and traitors walk.  We want 100% conviction rates.  That's what Pam spent her term doing.  She was investigating, impaneling grand juries and setting the table for the forthcoming trials.  Blanche is a stone cold killer.</p>\n<p>Timing here is important.  Trump needs the base energized for the mid-terms.  What better way to do this than toss some red meat out there with indictments arrests and trials of the people that have subverted and attacked this country the better part of 12 years now.  Trump NEVER forgets.</p>\n<p>He's going about this very  methodically and his timing is important.  I know you all get impatient with him and want this shit done like yesterday.  We understand.  However, there is a larger stategic play here.  Trust Trump.</p>\n<p>From now until the mid-terms will be very very interesting times.  Pay attention, Trump is always inside the OODA loop of the deep statists communists and RINOs.  Trust him.  He knows what he's doing.</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 23, "score_up": 26, "is_edited": true, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ASsUZTzTo", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 26, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8629974, "raw_c